WVSTOSTO.name: STORY HOTEL RIDDARGATAN
WVSTOSTO.description: The Story Hotel:  At the very heart of Stockholm. City Center location with quiet side street comfort.Extremely comfortable beds and the most original rooms. Completely newly renovated property, located near all sights, shops, events, offices, restaurants and bars.No-nonsense, but full-service. Self-check-in and checkout, allowing our hosts to focus all their attention on the guest. Free wireless Internet throughout the hotel. 24-hour room service.Story Bar & Restaurant is the lively meeting point for business or cocktails.Original art and prints available online.All rates include breakfast buffet!

WVSTOSTU.name: HOTEL DROTTNING KRISTINA STUREPLAN
WVSTOSTU.description: Staying at our hotel is an experience beyond the ordinary, the rooms and interiors are unique. With only 101 rooms Hotel Stureplan offers an exceptional level of personal service. Our concierge will open doors for you all over town when it comes to restaurants and nightclubs and any type of excursions you wish to take part in while visiting Stockholm.Room categories range from Cabin Rooms to Suites and executive floor, Stureplan Living. All rooms have bathrobes, minibar, free wireless internet access, safe, 24 hrs room service, tea & coffee facilities.Welcome to a hotel where excellent service is the minimum standard.

EREVMAX.07119.name: Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central
EREVMAX.07119.description: The Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central enjoys a fabulous location right next to Stockholm Central Station. The citys amazing range of restaurants, shops, museums and nightclubs are all within easy reach! This is a cash-free hotel. The Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central is located within Stockholms World Trade Center, with a direct link to Stockholm Central Station. Stockholms amazing restaurants, shopping, night clubs and sights are all within easy walking distance. If you arrive by car, you can easily park in the parking garage right next door to the hotel.

otherPolicies.Others: The Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central is a cash-free hotel. Credit Cards accepted:
otherPolicies.child_policy: Children up-to 9 years can stay free with existing bed.
otherPolicies.Terms & Condition: Guests are required to show a photo identification and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.
otherPolicies.parking_shuttle: NIf you arrive by car, we recommend that you park in the garage located in the same building as Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central. The price is SEK 280 per day, every day of the week.
otherPolicies.pet_policy: At Comfort Hotel Xpress Stockholm Central we also welcome your four-legged friends. For SEK 250 extra per visit they can stay with you at the hotel. Guide dogs are of course welcome at no extra charge. But remember to tell us when you make your reservation, so that we can find a suitable room for you and your dog
